Summary:	MooseFS - distributed, fault tolerant file system
Name:		moosefs
Version:	3.0.84
Release:	1%{?_relname}
License:	commercial
Group:		System Environment/Daemons
URL:		http://www.moosefs.com/
Source0:	%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
BuildRequires:	fuse-devel
